libs.content: find_program (dpkg_program dpkg doc "dpkg program of debian-based systems")

find_library(
        dab_libraries
        names dab_lib
        hints ${dab_dir}/lib
              ${dab_dir}/lib64
              ${libdab_pkg_library_dirs}
        paths /usr/lib
              /usr/lib64
              /usr/local/lib
              /usr/local/lib64
    )

find_library(
        sgp4_libraries
        names sgp4s
        hints ${sgp4_dir}/lib
        paths /usr/local/lib
              /usr/lib
              /usr/lib64
    )

find_library(
    hidapi_undecorated_library
    names libhidapi.a
    paths "${hidapi_root_dir}"
    path_suffixes lib)

find_library(
    hidapi_libusb_library
    names libhidapi.a libhidapi-libusb.a
    paths "${hidapi_root_dir}"
    path_suffixes lib
    hints ${pc_hidapi_libusb_library_dirs})

find_library(cm256cc_libraries
        names cm256cc libcm256cc
        hints ${cm256cc_dir}/lib
              ${cm256cc_dir}/lib64
              ${pc_cm256cc_libdir}
              ${cmake_install_prefix}/lib
              ${cmake_install_prefix}/lib64
        paths /usr/local/lib
              /usr/local/lib64
              /usr/lib
              /usr/lib64
    )

find_library(
    fftw3f_libraries
    names fftw3f libfftw3f
    hints $env{fftw3_dir}/lib
        ${pc_fftw3f_libdir}
    paths /usr/local/lib
          /usr/lib
          /usr/lib64
)

find_library(
    fftw3f_threads_libraries
    names fftw3f_threads libfftw3f_threads
    hints $env{fftw3_dir}/lib
        ${pc_fftw3f_libdir}
    paths /usr/local/lib
          /usr/lib
          /usr/lib64
)

find_library(
        apt_libraries
        names apt
        hints ${apt_dir}/lib
        paths /usr/local/lib
              /usr/lib
              /usr/lib64
    )

find_library(codec2_libraries
        names codec2 libcodec2
        hints ${codec2_dir}/lib
              ${codec2_dir}/lib64
              ${pc_codec2_libdir}
              ${cmake_install_prefix}/lib
              ${cmake_install_prefix}/lib64
        paths /usr/local/lib
              /usr/local/lib64
              /usr/lib
              /usr/lib64
    )

find_library(
        faad_library
        names faad
        hints ${faad_dir}/lib
              ${pc_faad_library_dirs}
        paths /usr/local/lib
              /usr/lib
              /usr/lib64
    )

find_library(
        uhd_libraries
        names uhd
        hints ${uhd_dir}/lib
        paths /usr/local/lib
              /usr/lib
              /usr/lib64
    )

find_library(lz4_libraries
    names lz4 liblz4
    hints ${pc_lz4_libdir}
          ${cmake_install_prefix}/lib
          ${cmake_install_prefix}/lib64
    paths ${lz4_include_dirs}/../lib
          /usr/local/lib
          /usr/lib
)

find_library(
        sdrplay_libraries
        names sdrplay_api
        hints ${sdrplay_dir}/x86_64
        paths /usr/local/lib
              /usr/lib
              /usr/lib64
    )
